sentences.english: Are air conditioning intakes which may permit the entry of cargo vapours closed?
sentences.chinese: 有可能吸入货物蒸汽的空调系统进气口是否已关闭？

sentences.english: When returning a cylinder to storage, the valve outlet seal must be installed leak-tight.

sentences.english: This expansion ratio also allows atmospheres of oxygen-enriched air to form in the area surrounding a release.

sentences.english: Leakage can occur at the valve outlet, due to leak-through at the seat.
sentences.chinese: 由于阀座泄漏，泄漏可能在阀门排气口发生。

sentences.english: The ramp sits at an acute angle to deflect the intake airstream from the longitudinal direction.
sentences.chinese: 这个斜面锐角使进气口的气流纵向流变。

sentences.english: Water must not drip continuously from vent.
sentences.chinese: 从排气口处必须没有水持续滴漏。

sentences.english: Larger air intakes and odd - shaped fog lights are built into the front bumper.
sentences.chinese: 更大的进气口和奇形雾灯，内置的前保险杠。

sentences.english: Are air conditioning intakes which may permit entry of cargo vapors closed?
sentences.chinese: 可能导致液货气体引入冷气系统之入气口已关闭？

sentences.english: The holes are made in the center of its bottom and along the periphery of its bottom to form an exhaust port.

sentences.english: Open the second sterile pouch and connect the tubing to the insufflator's gas outlet.

sentences.english: If water drips continuously from vent, second check is leaking.

sentences.english: The Canadian model also had daytime running lights located in the lower vent holes.
